data.description: Price improvement with seller incentive of $6,000. Welcome to your new home! Whether you are a first-time homebuyer, downsizing, or looking for an investment property, this cute and cozy bungalow is a fantastic opportunity. Walk into this cozy, all original flooring home. This adorable two bedroom with one bath is a perfect blend of comfort and style. Discover a cozy and inviting interior that feels like home from the moment you step in. The lovely backyard provides the perfect space for outdoor activities and relaxation. This City of East Point gem is conveniently located near shops, dining, and entertainment options and is only moments away from The Mercedes Benz Stadium and State Farm Arena. This home is ready to welcome its new owner. Home has a new roof 2023 and a fairly new HVAC system 2020. Kitchen features granite and all appliances including washer and dryer shall remain with property. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home sweet home. Your client will be happy you showed them this cute gem. Thank you for showing.    Property is Agent-owned. Seller is related to Listing Agent.
